{"id":110434,"type":2,"name":"Dragons: Gift of the Night Fury","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/4f/d3/110434_aZst8.jpg","rating":{"total":44,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":14,"7":18,"8":10,"9":0,"10":1},"score":6.9},"summary":"       远在北欧大海中央的博克岛，即将迎来一年一度的快乐圣诞节。希卡普和他的好朋友无牙一如既往，在博克岛的上空自由翱翔。可是，突然天空布满了各种各样的龙，甚至连岛上的龙也振翅高飞随这群龙远去。岛民们非常失落，但也只能面对龙离去的事实。未过多久，连无牙也在某个机缘下振翅高飞。过了数日，无牙始终没有返回，这令希卡普非常失落。某天，他被夺门而出的胖龙Meatlug撞到空中，继而随着它来到了一片陌生的小岛。在那里，希卡普发现了所有失踪的龙，也明白了他们离开博克岛的原因…… \r\n　　而他的好朋友无牙究竟又在哪里呢？ ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>驯龙高手番外篇：龙的礼物</li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/6836\">DreamWorks Animation</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>2011-11-15</li><li><span>片长: </span>22min</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>www.howtotrainyourdragon.com</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li>","collection":{"wish":16,"collect":77,"on_hold":1,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":15},{"name":"梦工厂","count":14},{"name":"短片","count":10},{"name":"美国","count":8},{"name":"2011","count":4},{"name":"OVA","count":4},{"name":"电影","count":2},{"name":"8WA","count":2},{"name":"DreamWorks","count":2},{"name":"2011年秋","count":1},{"name":"动画电影","count":1},{"name":"原创","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":858610,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/858610","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"Dragons: Gift of the Night Fury","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"crt":[{"id":73431,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ef/58/73431_crt_OqjhZ.jpg","name":"没牙仔","desc":"主角"}],"staff":[{"id":6836,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/55/2d/6836_prsn_NWb54.jpg","name":"梦工厂动画","desc":"动画制作"}],"relations":[{"id":13295,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/32/7e/13295_ilJ2B.jpg","title":"How to Train Your Dragon","type":"主线故事","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/13295"}]}